{
  "stem": "4361.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this wonderful woman contacted me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was partly involved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she told me what I wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But she also sent me a book of her poems.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she describes-- and she-- she was in the Vilna Ghetto with her mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she describes a very similar scene, that they were liberated, and-- I mean, this is so many years later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it's liberation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she's there with her mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the SS are being driven by-- by the Russian soldiers now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Russian soldiers, they didn't go for too many niceties.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't wait for Nuremberg tribunals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They did what they had to do whenever they had to do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if former victims of Nazi persecution would do something to them, he would let them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this girl, the writer of this poem, wants to go and do something to the SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the poem says that the mother put her hand on the daughter and said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means, 'For us Jews, it's not the right thing to do to take revenge.' I look back at-- at-- the poem is always associated with my standing on-- on that hill behind barbed wire, yelling at the SS, 'verfluchte SS.' That's all I did.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Cursed SS.' 'Verfluchte' means cursed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next thing that happened when all the SS were gone, everybody descended on the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were women eating marmalade with onions, sugar with-- I mean, it was just-- just incredible because the first thing was food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next thing, in the afternoon, about four Frenchmen in a truck came over to the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, by this time, there was nobody around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The camp gates were open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said that yes, the Russians are indeed approaching.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
